      <odd id="aspace_483ae9b17c7590e0ae6942be6e432fba">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 21-F (YRG 21-F), Student records of the Yale Divinity School.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_8dbb0df1d03204b1a57b5a29681c4dde">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were transferred from the registrar of the Yale Divinity School, 2002-2012.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_a194feeb8760c4d63fd4901dc04fa640">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>While this collection as a whole is available for research, parts of it may be restricted due to law, university policy or fragility. Any restricted material will be noted as such.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_59caef34ca05c3811a1ad61e288083e1">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Divinity School, Yale University, Student Records (RU 913). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_d7e6c616cd4da6206ad5ec9b512fc446">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged by accession.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_32942338befdb0b60f620d8a0ceac1bc">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of letters, application forms, transcripts, notes, recommendations, and evaluations documenting students of the Yale Divinity School.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_5dfdc425b33dfc8d9922506946157f12">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>Some records in this finding aid have been redacted, as they include student names, donor names, and other restricted data. These records will not appear in the published finding aid.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
